<br>
<br>
Very similar beggers were bothering me, one in particular in this case.  I told him would give him plat, but he had to meet me in the Arena.  <br>
<br>
Begger1 &quot;but your just going to kill me.&quot;<br>
Eandori &quot;Maybe, but I WILL give you plat.  I promise that.&quot;<br>
Begger1 &quot;you promise you'll give me money?&quot;<br>
Eandori &quot;sure&quot;<br>
so the begger steps into the arena and walks all the way to the other side to receive his 20 plat.  Immediately after I hand it to him, I /pet attack and kill him.<br>
Begger1 &quot;DUDE, you killed me!&quot;<br>
Begger1 &quot;that was not cool&quot;<br>
Eandori &quot;but I gave you 20 plat, that's a ton for a level 5 newbie, anyways it's still here on your corpse&quot;<br>
So the begger steps back into the arena after finding his way back.  just after he loots his corpse I nuke him for 1000.<br>
Begger1 &quot;WTF YOU ASS?!?&quot;<br>
Eandori &quot;.....&quot;<br>
<br>
So he runs in and tries to drag his corpse, loot it, etc for a little while longer.  I killed him a few more times then finally let him have his plat back.  I figured I had my fun and felt the 20 plat as well worth it. <p><!--EZCODE CENTER START--><div style="text-align:center">Master Eandori Raintree<br>
