<br>
When you go into magelo, its possible to set up a 'fake inventory' and hide your bank and money from public view.<br>
<br>
Considering we've got posts today on how to handle beggars/con-artists, you don't want people knowing how much plat you're carrying around. <!--EZCODE EMOTICON START ;) --><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/intl/aenglish/images/emoticons/wink.gif ALT=";)"><!--EZCODE EMOTICON END--> <br>
<br>
The fake inventory is nice, as you can display prominent items like focus items or resist gear, but you don't have to worry about people seeing that you were sloppy one afternoon about organizing your gear, or seeing how many stacks of dark-elf parts you like to carry around. <!--EZCODE EMOTICON START :) --><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/intl/aenglish/images/emoticons/smile.gif ALT=":)"><!--EZCODE EMOTICON END-->  <p><!--EZCODE LINK START--><a href="http://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=381929"> Naladini </a><!--EZCODE LINK END--><br>
